<div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 text-right order-2 md:order-1">
<div class="glass-panel p-4 rounded-xl text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-tighter text-on-secondary-container inline-block">
                                        S2k-Leitlinie "Lumbale Radikulopathie"
                                    </div>
</div>
<div class="z-10 bg-primary w-4 h-4 rounded-full ring-8 ring-primary-fixed/30 order-1 md:order-2"></div>
<div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 order-3">
<h4 class="font-headline text-lg text-primary">Therapieentscheidung</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface/60">Multimodale konservative Therapie für mindestens 6 Wochen bei fehlender neurologischer Progredienz.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Blockquote -->
<blockquote class="glass-panel border-l-8 border-secondary rounded-xl p-10 my-16 shadow-xl italic font-serif text-2xl text-on-surface/80 leading-relaxed">
                        "Die chirurgische Indikation muss heute kritischer gestellt werden als noch vor einem Jahrzehnt. Die Biologie heilt oft das, was das Messer nur erzwingen will."
                        <cite class="block not-italic font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold text-secondary mt-6">— Dr. Adrian Volckmans, Lead Surgeon</cite>
</blockquote>
<!-- Table Section -->
<div class="my-16 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low shadow-sm border border-black/5">
<div class="glass-panel px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center rounded-t-2xl border-none">
<h3 class="font-headline text-xl text-primary">Indikationsmatrix Chirurgie</h3>
<span class="text-[10px] font-mono opacity-50">TAB_IND_01</span>
</div>
<table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
<thead>
<tr class="bg-surface-container-high/50 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface/50">
<th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Symptomatik</th>
<th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Empfehlung</th>
<th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Dringlichkeit</th>
</tr>
